data.description: Gorgeous newer custom home on over 1.5 impeccably maintained acres, The best of both worlds, this home offers peaceful country living and privacy but still less than 20 minutes from UNC. When you step inside you'll notice tons of natural light! Formal dining room plus large open kitchen with breakfast nook. Cozy gas fireplace in a spacious family room. Such a great open layout for entertaining! Upstairs you'll find the MBR with walk in closet, and a completely remodeled custom bathroom. Great sized secondary bedrooms plus a big bonus room.Super versatile space! Enjoy your private backyard on the screen porch on all of our beautiful Carolina days. All appliances stay! This one is a gem!
